MANY ACCEPT BIDS
OF VARIOUS FRATS

SIGMA NU LEADS WITH
18 DELTA MU IS
NEXT WITH 17

Approximately 180 bids were is-
sued this year in the annual pledging
campaign. Of this number over
100 Freshmen decided they wanted
to be fraternity men.
Sigma Nu of the national group
headed the list in number of
pledges having captured 18. Della
Mu topped the locals with 17.
